Item.LongDesc:
Tolerance for the refining steps
               for each of the best subsets
               The default value is 1e-8;

Item.MATLABcode:
n=200;
p=3;
randn('state', 123456);
X=randn(n,p);
% Uncontaminated data
y=randn(n,1);
% Contaminated data
ycont=y;
ycont(1:5)=ycont(1:5)+6;
[out]=Taureg(ycont,X);

